Me, too.

5
00:00:49,369 --> 00:00:50,167
Mm.

6
00:00:54,667 --> 00:00:56,357
I'll see you 
at the scene, sexy.

7
00:00:56,358 --> 00:00:57,306
Okay.

8
00:01:02,795 --> 00:01:04,279
Javier Esposito.
Mm-hmm.

9
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:07,216
When we get to this crime scene,
do not wink at me,

10
00:01:07,217 --> 00:01:08,289
do not smile at me,

11
00:01:08,290 --> 00:01:12,303
and don't even look at me with
those puppy dog eyes. Got it?

12
